// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/DdX3zH space frame tower by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/7tGBD3 space frame

// Used https://www.shadertoy.com/view/XtSczV Rotational symmetry by iq
// to create a tower of space frame beams.

// Trying how complex the space-frame structures can get by constructing a tower (could be some kind of industrial tank).
// Performance is not an issue even with large constructs, but flickering becomes a problem (had to use thicker grids for large structure).

// tags: 3d, grid, space, repetition, tower, polar, mesh, architecture, construction, frame, building, limited, truss, industrial, struts

